4e81263afa0d3c58316e8104f9c155f0c11946fae7a9fa98ff3d86637e56be377fe584ca82df0786f4c74a180813cbcf87f25e0ee7bbbea9073eac20660f08d9  fix-build-without-NLS.patch
"
